n<br />\n<span class=\"large\"><span class=\"brown\"><strong>所以，與其數下有幾多諻語入左香港，不如努力推廣本地文化。</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n不用太灰，其實香港都出口好多官方被迫認證的詞語：<br />\n「攬炒」、「光復」<br />\n<br />\n別怕，永遠高文明的地方文化係會同化低文明的地方。"},{"pid":"da100bf8326632c5cbc30d4b28395b1747ad3c6c","tid":2112809,"uid":245849,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4fe0d4b52ffa519ed39fea9176750f942ff70c5d","tid":2112809,"uid":179409,"like":7,"dislike":5,"score":2,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T15:21:47.000Z","msg":"之前都同人嘈過<br />\n叫人唔好再用「優化」<br />\n用「改善」、「改良」、「改進」<br />\n有人死拗話意思唔係完全一樣<br />\n我反而想問<br />\n點解一定要完全一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n從來無人答到我<br />\n只係俾我覺得香港人用字好自卑<br />\n中國人用字意思唔完全跟足香港人<br />\n中國人係唔會在意<br />\n但係香港人用字意思唔完全跟足中國人<br />\n香港人就好似覺得自己唔啱咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真係痴撚線"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T17:11:53.000Z","msg":"我講開Fine Tune...."},{"pid":"63a44f9a6eb05469406f30dd62c275844e5f4828","tid":2112809,"uid":158270,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"901da9a429801bcf4ecb3d1a96e5cdb3ed211111","tid":2112809,"uid":112748,"like":6,"dislike":3,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"e412af546c110bda1d4c9053c9de886eb49b31f6","tid":2112809,"uid":204929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T15:04:33.000Z","msg":"睇咗段片先,再拉落下面睇我評論,以獨立思考!<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/1OcOkpVY02o\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F1OcOkpVY02o&d=6SBmejzB2pOSQzgprEhHpSvUjXV925tPaxuyg6D%2B4Js%3D&h=2cadd6b0\" data-auto-link ta